      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STRIKE IT BELLE (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (28.34) in an A4 at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. BERETTA MAKALA (1) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 18 from 36 starts. Filled a minor placings again last time when third (28.11) at this track making it six placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to feature again. PLACEINMYHEART (2) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 7 lengths away in second (27.97) at this track in an A4 over 450m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to feature again. BARNFIELD CHIEF (6) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
